<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 26 Dec 2024 06:20:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国将在西藏建设世界最大水电站</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-build-worlds-largest-hydropower-dam-tibet-2024-12-26/</link><description>中国已批准建设世界上最大的水电大坝，在青藏高原东缘启动了一项雄心勃勃的项目，该项目可能会影响印度和孟加拉国下游数百万人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Dec 2024 05:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-build-worlds-largest-hydropower-dam-tibet-2024-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统府首次举办兵棋模拟中国紧急情况</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/first-taiwans-presidential-office-runs-war-games-simulate-china-emergency-2024-12-26/</link><description>几位了解情况的官员表示，台湾总统府进行了首次桌面演习，模拟与中国的军事升级，此时台湾正面临新的中国军事威胁。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Dec 2024 04:10:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/first-taiwans-presidential-office-runs-war-games-simulate-china-emergency-2024-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>美元保持弹性，亚洲股市受到节日提振</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-26/</link><description>周四，亚洲股市在假期清淡的交易中小幅上涨，延续了本周早些时候的涨幅，几乎没有消息或数据改变其走势，而美元则徘徊在两年高点附近。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Dec 2024 02:26:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>由于希望中国采取更多刺激措施，油价小幅上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-edge-higher-hopes-more-china-stimulus-2024-12-26/</link><description>周四，由于全球最大石油进口国中国出台额外财政刺激措施的希望，油价在假期交投清淡的情况下小幅走高，而美国原油库存的预期下降也提供了支撑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Dec 2024 02:04:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-edge-higher-hopes-more-china-stimulus-2024-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>台湾国防部警告新资助法对安全造成“严重影响”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-defence-ministry-warns-serious-impact-security-under-new-funding-laws-2024-12-26/</link><description>台湾国防部警告称，在台湾面临中国军事威胁加剧之际，反对党通过了要求削减约 800 亿新台币（合 24.5 亿美元）国防开支的法律，这将给安全带来“严重影响”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Dec 2024 01:09:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-defence-ministry-warns-serious-impact-security-under-new-funding-laws-2024-12-26/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普提名迈阿密戴德郡官员担任驻巴拿马大使</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-nominates-miami-dade-official-ambassador-panama-2024-12-25/</link><description>美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普周三提名迈阿密戴德县专员凯文·马里诺·卡布雷拉担任驻巴拿马大使。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 20:52:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-nominates-miami-dade-official-ambassador-panama-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>刚果释放了大部分因非法采矿而被关押的中国男子</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/congo-frees-most-chinese-men-held-illegal-mining-2024-12-25/</link><description>刚果民主共和国当局周二晚间表示，因涉嫌在该国经营非法金矿而被捕的 17 名中国男子中，有 14 人已获释。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 09:58:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/congo-frees-most-chinese-men-held-illegal-mining-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国平安夜票房跌至13年新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-christmas-eve-box-office-plunges-13-year-low-2024-12-25/</link><description>票务预订平台猫眼周三的数据显示，中国平安夜票房收入暴跌至至少13年来的最低水平。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 09:09:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-christmas-eve-box-office-plunges-13-year-low-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国对欧盟白兰地反倾销调查再延长三个月</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-extends-eu-brandy-anti-dumping-investigation-2024-12-25/</link><description>中国商务部周三表示，将对原产于欧盟的白兰地的反倾销调查延长三个月，低于此前指导意见允许的全部延长期限。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 07:52:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-extends-eu-brandy-anti-dumping-investigation-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国骗子从鱿鱼游戏中汲取灵感，对负债者进行掠夺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-tricksters-take-cue-squid-game-prey-indebted-2024-12-25/</link><description>在中国的“鱿鱼游戏”中，诈骗者通过承诺奖金、债务重组和其他并非总是兑现承诺的计划，以经济衰退中陷入财务困境的人为目标。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 06:29:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-tricksters-take-cue-squid-game-prey-indebted-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>巴西中场奥斯卡重返圣保罗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/brazilian-midfielder-oscar-returns-sao-paulo-2024-12-25/</link><description>巴西意甲球队周二表示，前切尔西中场球员奥斯卡将以三年合同回到他的前俱乐部圣保罗。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 04:38:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/brazilian-midfielder-oscar-returns-sao-paulo-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>尽管销量增长，丰田全球产量连续第十个月下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-global-production-down-10th-month-despite-rising-sales-2024-12-25/</link><description>日本汽车制造商丰田汽车周三表示，尽管由于美国和中国需求强劲，其全球销量连续第二个月增长，但该公司 11 月份全球产量连续第 10 个月下降。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 04:34:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-global-production-down-10th-month-despite-rising-sales-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中方谴责菲律宾防长就中美导弹问题发表言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-condemns-philippine-defence-chiefs-remarks-china-us-missiles-2024-12-25/</link><description>中国周三谴责菲律宾国防部长有关中国的言论，称其为“毫无根据的指控”，“恶意攻击”中国执政的共产党。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 03:57:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-condemns-philippine-defence-chiefs-remarks-china-us-missiles-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中日外长同意访日安全对话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-foreign-ministers-meet-beijing-seafood-trade-agenda-2024-12-25/</link><description>日本周三表示，中日外长在北京举行的会谈为日本明年接待中国外长以及双方同意尽快举行安全对话铺平了道路。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 01:03:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-foreign-ministers-meet-beijing-seafood-trade-agenda-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大谴责中国就维吾尔族和西藏问题针对加拿大机构采取的措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-condemns-chinas-steps-against-canadian-institutions-over-uyghurs-tibet-2024-12-24/</link><description>加拿大政府周二谴责中国对涉及维吾尔族和西藏人权问题的两家加拿大机构和20名人士采取措施。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 21:43:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-condemns-chinas-steps-against-canadian-institutions-over-uyghurs-tibet-2024-12-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>